data.description: Welcome to 4429 W Rose Ln in Glendale, AZ! This beautiful move-in ready home is a true gem, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. With its vaulted ceilings and spacious layout, this home is sure to impress. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, there is plenty of space for a growing family or those who love to entertain. The split floor plan has  numerous upgrades including Roof, HVAC, Tile & laminate flooring, Bathrooms, Downstairs Plumbing and Pool Re-Plastering all done in 2019. This Glendale Gem is waiting for You! Let's make this house your home!
